ENUGU-  Tragedy occurred on Saturday in Oruku community in Nkanu East Local Government Area in Enugu state when unidentified men shot dead the traditional ruler of the community Igwe Emmanuel Chidebere Mba. The incident which thrown the community into mourning led to protest by aggrieved members in the community while houses and properties believed to belong to those behind the ugly incident were set ablaze. It was alleged that some men dressed in a police uniform drove into the community in an SUV on saturday evening while the monarch was having a meeting with his subjects at the town hall. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYINGÂ THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! An eye witnessed account told our correspondent that the the alleged policemen demanded to see the traditional ruler and when the traditional ruler was identified, one of the men shot at him and he fell down bleeding. According to him, there was pandemonium in the community as a result of the gun shot as residents scampered for safety Police Arrest Village Head, 10 Others For Alleged Banditry In Niger State Lagos Impounds 60 Vehicles For Traffic Offences Chrcks further revealed that the monarch was rushed to the hospital for treatment but was confirm dead by a doctor at the National Orthopedic hospital . It was learnt that corps of the late monarch has been deposited at National Orthopedic hospital mortuary. As a results of the Mornach death, aggrieved members of the community embarked on protest on sunday morning, burning and destroying houses believed to belong to those behind the incident. Our correspondent learnt that over 6 houses and several vehicles have been destroyed in Oruku community while some other building are still on fire as of the time of filling this report When contacted the PPRO of Enugu State Police Command Daniel Ndukwe, said the situation in Oruku community has been brought under control & the CP has directed a full-scale investigation to unravel the cause of the incidence, arrest and prosecute anyone found wanting. He further calls on people of the Community to remain calm & eschew acts capable of further breaching the peace in the area, as anyone caught will be made to face the full weight of the law. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION